8. **Two stray `console.log`s** in `app.js` (~5620, ~6015) from the schedule sweep diagnostics.
9. **Appwrite books that don't match a hardcoded genre chip** ŌĆö only show in the "All" tab. Their `tags` are still searchable but won't surface via the chip UI.
